				<h2>Research Strengths</h2>
				<p>
Our key strengths lie in cancer genomics, DNA damage, RNA biology, and drug development.</p>

<p>We are also building expertise in drug delivery, with a focus on nanotechnology-driven approaches for delivering small RNA mimics and inhibitors.</p>

<p>The Pediatric Translational Working Group, established under the Mays Cancer Center P30, meets regularly to collaborate on translating discoveries into innovative therapies.
				</p>
